code: public static void verify(File file, String entry) throws Exception {     try (ZipFile zipFile = new ZipFile(file)) {         Enumeration<? extends ZipEntry> entries = zipFile.entries().         while (entries.hasMoreElements()) {             if (entries.nextElement().getName().equals(entry)) {                 return.             }         }         throw new AssertionError("No entry " + entry).     } }
